WEBVTT

00:00:01.800 --> 00:00:06.639
All right. Good morning, almost afternoon, family. Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:10.970
We're going to go over some of the things we see in the news real quick and then we'll jump in the river.

00:00:10.971 --> 00:00:18.418
We're going to pray for President Trump because he's headed to Turkey, and we're going to pray for him for this meeting, whatever he's doing.

00:00:18.419 --> 00:00:26.399
We're going to cover him, his plane, and everything he eats; we have to cover him in prayer.

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:32.216
He'll be there for, I think, three days, so we're going to cover him the whole time he's there.

00:00:32.217 --> 00:00:36.346
We have assignments, you know, and so we're going to pray over our nation.

00:00:36.347 --> 00:00:45.419
But isn't Jesus wonderful? There were no major shootings or anything for the Fourth of July.

00:00:45.420 --> 00:00:52.559
I don't think we had much; I think we only had one little bit of a little something, but it was nothing at all.

00:00:52.560 --> 00:00:58.709
The hand of the Lord protected our nation, and you could sense it as we were praying.

00:00:58.710 --> 00:01:07.279
There was a disturbance—I could feel it very strong all afternoon on the 4th, interceding for the firework shows.

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:12.452
But what I think is amazing is what happened regarding the firework shows.

00:01:12.453 --> 00:01:26.079
I believe there was divine intervention for the fireworks shows concerning the mass casualties, shootings, and things like that.

00:01:26.080 --> 00:01:35.458
As we see, go ahead and show all that happened. This is not normal.

00:01:35.459 --> 00:01:47.039
43 major firework shows were cancelled across America, and they had to reschedule or delay.

00:01:47.040 --> 00:02:01.812
43 major cities. That's not normal. Philadelphia, Chicago—go ahead and show them the list.

00:02:01.813 --> 00:02:08.478
Oh, okay, you didn't get a list? That's what I asked you before we started.

00:02:08.479 --> 00:02:18.879
I said, 'Don't start until you have that list of all the cities.'All right, it's fine. For one, Washington D.C. was a major one.

00:02:18.880 --> 00:02:26.879
There were over 300,000 people that had gathered to watch the fireworks shows and the massive celebration.

00:02:26.880 --> 00:02:30.878
Then a storm came out of nowhere with lightning and everything.

00:02:30.879 --> 00:02:36.248
Everybody, they were telling, 'Get out of here.'They were flipping the tables over and making all the people leave.

00:02:36.249 --> 00:02:51.102
So they went on and had the fireworks show, I think at midnight or 1:00 AM, and only 100,000 people out of the 300,000 showed up to come watch it again.

00:02:51.103 --> 00:03:00.559
This is the District; this is where they cancelled the District. I know, but I was looking for...

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:04.318
do you have any little videos of the people saying they cancelled it?

00:03:04.319 --> 00:03:10.829
There was one in Chicago that was delayed. Philadelphia...

00:03:10.830 --> 00:03:17.918
I thought the big ones, because the Lord specifically told us to pray over Philadelphia.

00:03:17.919 --> 00:03:21.999
Boston, Massachusetts. Praying over Boston. The Lord said, 'Pray over Boston.'And I kept interceding.

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:28.387
I prayed for Boston a lot and for the Red Sox, and there was stuff that got cancelled.

00:03:28.388 --> 00:03:37.438
What is this right here? This is a Boston concert and fireworks.

00:03:37.439 --> 00:03:42.262
Show them that. So all the Boston fireworks got cancelled or delayed.

00:03:42.263 --> 00:03:57.259
I don't know if it was completely cancelled or if they went ahead and did it, but even all over the state of Oklahoma, a massive storm came in at 8:00 with 80 mph winds—90—blew trees over.

00:03:57.260 --> 00:04:03.625
It was bad. It came out of nowhere. People say, 'Well, that's destructive.'Well, it's divine delays.

00:04:03.626 --> 00:04:07.465
Regardless, people are going to do what they want to do; they're thick-headed.

00:04:07.466 --> 00:04:11.679
But the Lord's trying to show you there's something to this.

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:27.009
The storms came in with 80 mile per hour winds over Oklahoma, blew all through Tulsa, Oklahoma City, Edmond, and they cancelled a lot of firework shows.

00:04:27.010 --> 00:04:32.159
I don't know if they went ahead and redid them, but the terror in the heartland...

00:04:32.160 --> 00:04:39.599
praying over the heartland. So they didn't have anything, and it was all done away with.

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:44.159
Then we have Washington D.C. It was major, and so it's very interesting to me.

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:53.519
Even New York City had stuff going on. Go ahead. Can you show some of it?

00:04:53.520 --> 00:04:58.699
This is what the whole focus was today: to give God glory. This is what I was trying to show them.

00:04:58.700 --> 00:05:07.319
Giving God glory for why I believe this was prayer. 'Welcome back to America 250. Events are being delayed in D.C.

00:05:07.320 --> 00:05:18.986
because of that bad weather.'A spokesperson just moments ago from Freedom 250 putting out a statement saying, 'The safety of our guests, performers, and staff is our top priority due to approaching severe storms.

00:05:18.987 --> 00:05:37.539
Freedom 250, the U.S. Secret Service, the Park Service, and National Park Service are asking guests to evacuate event grounds and seek temporary shelter in a nearby area.'We will continue to follow this as you look live over the Mall.

00:05:37.540 --> 00:05:42.799
It doesn't look like everyone's leaving, but apparently, there are some approaching dangerous storms.

00:05:42.800 --> 00:05:51.559
So we'll keep you posted. Meanwhile, down in South Carolina in the Lowcountry, it is looking much better.

00:05:51.560 --> 00:05:58.079
Madison Scarpino is there; they cancelled the parade because of excessive heat.

00:05:58.080 --> 00:06:03.179
So the parade that we were praying over got cancelled because of the weather. They didn't even have the parade.

00:06:03.180 --> 00:06:17.359
More than 73 million Americans along the East Coast on this Fourth of July are under extreme heat alerts today, and that is causing delays or outright cancellations of several Fourth of July events.

00:06:17.360 --> 00:06:20.559
Independence Day parades in Philadelphia and Washington D.C.

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:24.399
have actually been scrapped. Temperatures are just too dangerously high.

00:06:24.400 --> 00:06:38.199
The Great American State Fair will reopen today. No fireworks in some cities.

00:06:38.200 --> 00:06:46.822
Yes, I didn't know that. That's interesting. So on and on. But it's just interesting.

00:06:46.823 --> 00:07:07.369
I thought, 'How is this going as I was praying for the FBI, Homeland Security, and the CIA—all our law enforcement—to uncover and discover basically any plots, plans, or pursuits across this land?'Praying over these areas for no mass casualties.

00:07:07.370 --> 00:07:16.159
And I thought it was interesting because so many things were cancelled because of thunderstorms.

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:26.490
I thought that's wild. Do you have more to show them? Well, show me Philadelphia.

00:07:26.491 --> 00:07:32.159
What about the one in Chicago? You talked about Chicago. If you don't, that's fine.

00:07:32.160 --> 00:07:48.359
I'm going to move on. Was there anything else you wanted to show today? We see the Islamic...

00:07:48.360 --> 00:08:09.598
they had the big funeral and throughout the 4th of July, they kept having huge massive gatherings in Iran for Death to America, chanting 'Death to America,'mad at America—all the things that are going on for our 250th anniversary for our country.

00:08:09.599 --> 00:08:26.665
They were saying all these major things for the funeral for Ayatollah Khamenei. Do you have some of that? Yes. See that? Go ahead.

00:08:26.666 --> 00:08:37.233
I wonder if these people are really grieving or if they're like the people of North Korea, where they're forced to, and if you don't act out, you're tortured or hurt really bad.

00:08:37.234 --> 00:08:41.518
I wonder sometimes if they really knew him and if they were really grieving about this guy.

00:08:41.519 --> 00:09:00.079
Some of them are in little boxes. I wonder who's in the box. I think it's cremated or something.

00:09:00.080 --> 00:09:10.479
But Muslims don't get cremated, right? Is that just his pieces? That's weird.

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:23.999
So these are all the massive gatherings of the people just upset at America, saying 'Death to America.'And then they had the leader vow for revenge, calling for Trump's assassination.

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:29.639
They want him gone and they want somebody to take out our President.

00:09:29.640 --> 00:09:33.838
So their leader was saying that they wanted revenge about that.

00:09:33.839 --> 00:09:43.099
This man right here now. I don't know who this idiot is, but go ahead and play him. Can you hear him? Yes.

00:09:43.100 --> 00:09:49.492
Could you ever have imagined that one day we'd be praying over the body of our martyred Mr.

00:09:49.493 --> 00:09:54.250
Aname? I was just on my way here; I kept imagining that this wouldn't be the case.

00:09:54.251 --> 00:10:02.159
We've always come here for Eid prayers like this, and the way this happened is unbearable for anyone.

00:10:02.160 --> 00:10:12.079
He was one of a kind; there was no one like him. He touched all our hearts with his own heart. Now our hearts have stopped.

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:24.398
Reflect upon the tragic fate of Imam Hussein, the grandson of the prophet, peace be upon him, whose sacrifice remains a powerful symbol of justice and courage for all people.

00:10:24.399 --> 00:10:35.119
It's been 37 years; my whole life has been with him. In this way, God willing, God will help.

00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:42.341
The killers of our martyred Imam will not die a natural death, and the people will take this revenge.

00:10:42.342 --> 00:10:49.679
The system will take this revenge, and it's unimaginable that the killers of our leader would walk the earth alive.

00:10:49.680 --> 00:10:57.919
Revenge will be taken. That's all. So, we hear what they're saying, right?

00:10:57.920 --> 00:11:02.159
He said he wants revenge; they want revenge. And so, they're all calling out for revenge.

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:13.119
That's why I think it's even more of a miracle that on the 250th anniversary, we had nothing as far as a covering and all the storms.

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:18.319
And I thought, isn't this interesting? But as they're protesting, they're in the streets.

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:26.772
They're upset about it, and because of our anniversary, they have the bodies in glass.

00:11:26.773 --> 00:11:42.459
There's a lot of people; it says about 12 million. Twelve million people, wow.

00:11:42.460 --> 00:11:47.679
Twelve million people as they were grieving their president and their Ayatollah.

00:11:47.680 --> 00:12:00.759
So, they have things and they're throwing things at Trump. Do you understand why we're here today?

00:12:00.760 --> 00:12:08.105
He's going to be in Turkey on their turf, so we must pray a hedge of protection on this.

00:12:08.106 --> 00:12:15.439
I told you I saw the leader of Turkey as a vampire in the days ahead.

00:12:15.440 --> 00:12:21.039
He puts on a cloak and he will take over the Black Sea and the strait coming out of the Black Sea.

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:30.319
I saw them beating their war drums in the days ahead against Israel and for a strike coming against Damascus.

00:12:30.320 --> 00:12:42.479
I saw them beating their war drums and I saw them going to a wounded brother in the days ahead with Syria.

00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:50.638
They were going alongside Russia because of an escalation of war.

00:12:50.639 --> 00:13:10.719
Now, when I'm seeing the news now of what we saw back—was it this time last year—even some of the things the Lord has showed us over a year ago to pray about Turkey joining the war, Putin using unconventional weapons of war concerning Poland in the days ahead.

00:13:10.720 --> 00:13:29.039
I said I saw him shooting a new kind of missile. And the Lord I said, 'Is this nuclear?'And the Lord said, 'This is not nuclear, but it is a weapon that has never been used before.'This is a new type of weapon that's never been used before.

00:13:29.040 --> 00:13:47.225
And the Lord said, 'Watch Poland. Watch Warsaw. Watch this area, for there will be an escalation when Putin strikes Warsaw, Poland.'This will be the beginning of World War III of a major World War III.

00:13:47.226 --> 00:13:51.587
And I saw America join in with this and I saw an escalation of things.

00:13:51.588 --> 00:13:55.359
The Lord said, 'Pray for this.'Remember, does anybody remember?

00:13:55.360 --> 00:14:09.278
And I said, 'Watch Poland.'Do you see the headlines in the news? Yeah. So, Russia planning attack on Poland.

00:14:09.279 --> 00:14:40.119
And I said, when they strike Warsaw with a weapon that we've never seen before—and that's why I saw there would be a draft—I saw a draft for the United States of America because behind the scenes I saw North Korea being involved, Turkey being involved, and other allies concerning Russia to escalate using weapons that are bigger than the little rockets they're using right now.

00:14:40.120 --> 00:14:54.398
I saw major stuff and so here we see this: 'Polish PM warns critical months ahead and faces a Russia threat,'and this is what the Lord showed us over a year ago.

00:14:54.399 --> 00:15:00.799
I believe that's what it is. It's interesting because it's the same place.

00:15:00.800 --> 00:15:09.639
So we see in part; a lot of times I don't have a clue. That's why prophetic is hard to me and I always say I'm not prophetic.

00:15:09.640 --> 00:15:18.193
I see these things but I don't know the timing of it. He just gives me what I'm supposed to have to pray and I'm like, 'Wow.'And so, has it happened yet?

00:15:18.194 --> 00:15:29.728
No, it hasn't happened yet, but they're talking about it and there's rumblings of it and it's in the news. And I'm like, if what I saw comes to pass, it's bad.

00:15:29.729 --> 00:15:39.954
I saw the Tasmanian devil coming up out of the ground and I said, 'Who is this?'And he said, 'That's Apollyon.'And Apollyon came up out of the pit and started spinning around Putin.

00:15:39.955 --> 00:15:50.239
And I saw him over his thinking, oppress him with 'war, war, war.'And I saw Apollyon come up.

00:15:50.240 --> 00:15:56.319
And I saw an angel release the chains off of Apollyon. And Apollyon had a Viking outfit on.

00:15:56.320 --> 00:16:06.852
And he shot up out of the ground. He was being held captive in a chamber and they had massive chains on him.

00:16:06.853 --> 00:16:15.882
And I saw an angel release this demonic-looking thing with horns come up out of the ground and start spinning around. And he went right to Russia.

00:16:15.883 --> 00:16:29.599
And I heard 'war, war.'And I saw as I saw this, a darkness came upon his face—not on the angel, but on the demonic thing, on Putin.

00:16:29.600 --> 00:16:49.252
And then I saw them taking a bat signal with Hitler, trying to do satanic things to bring forth a Hitler spirit over Europe for a new World War III to turn into World War III.

00:16:49.253 --> 00:16:57.085
And I saw the old tanks and the old things all throughout England and all these areas because of finances and things.

00:16:57.086 --> 00:17:03.439
I saw major bankers that were behind this. They said, 'We want to bring forth the Mahdi.

00:17:03.440 --> 00:17:13.279
We want to bring forth the Antichrist, and it will come through war,'is what their plan was.

00:17:13.280 --> 00:17:21.861
And a plague—new plagues and famine and viruses and war go hand in hand.

00:17:21.862 --> 00:17:28.879
All of it go together: wars, plagues, famine, all this. And you saw it in writing.

00:17:28.880 --> 00:17:34.505
So, interesting, huh? So, we're seeing Poland now. And this is concerning Poland.

00:17:34.506 --> 00:17:40.809
The Lord said, 'Watch Warsaw.'And so, are we afraid of this? I'm not. I know Jesus is coming.

00:17:40.810 --> 00:17:44.219
I have an expectation for what's about to happen in my spirit.

00:17:44.220 --> 00:17:50.861
Jesus Christ is coming. And he is bringing forth right now his key faces.

00:17:50.862 --> 00:17:59.496
As I saw this in the spirit, I saw—and you know when I told you I saw—the Lord said, 'Don't hang around dead people.

00:17:59.497 --> 00:18:05.199
Don't hang around dead stuff and try to let them influence you.

00:18:05.200 --> 00:18:13.826
You influence them to come out of it.'Right? But I saw Ichabod on certain ministers'doorsteps.

00:18:13.827 --> 00:18:20.159
Ichabod because they have detached themselves from the life source.

00:18:20.160 --> 00:18:43.542
And as I was talking to one general yesterday, I saw blue coming off of the life source that looked like a sapphire that was attached to the umbilical cord of the navel of the belly of an individual.

00:18:43.543 --> 00:18:50.699
And the life source had a three-stranded cord in this that was coming out of the Father.

00:18:50.700 --> 00:18:57.644
As you were attached to the vine and you're the branch, you're attached to the vine.

00:18:57.645 --> 00:19:04.539
It was going down and it went into the individual. But as it was there, it was feeding life.

00:19:04.540 --> 00:19:09.839
Fresh Rhema, fresh revelation from him was coming as you are attached to him.

00:19:09.840 --> 00:19:15.146
But it was three: it was two on top—two of the cords were on top—and one was on the bottom.

00:19:15.147 --> 00:19:21.918
It went like this. And it was on a cord; a three-stranded cord is not easily broken.

00:19:21.919 --> 00:19:34.079
But as I saw a cord that was attached to you as a believer, if you're attached to the life source of Jesus, you are flourishing.

00:19:34.080 --> 00:19:44.332
But as I saw certain key figures of leaders who once were—I'll call it like that—have cut themselves off of the life source of him.

00:19:44.333 --> 00:19:50.798
They had that umbilical cord wrapped around their feet in this vision as I was praying this weekend.

00:19:50.799 --> 00:20:02.399
It was wrapped around the feet of the individuals that looked like something that was a yellow dried-up placenta cord, dead, lifeless, and it had an odor.

00:20:02.400 --> 00:20:13.918
And I saw flies by it. And the Lord said, "You can camp around what was dead or you can camp around what is alive. It's your choice.

00:20:13.919 --> 00:20:24.928
But if you keep camping around that which is dead, I have an Ichabod upon the doorstep."He said that will rub off on you.

00:20:24.929 --> 00:20:37.599
I saw certain things. The Lord warned me. I saw people who were alive, and that fire was a blue flame that was coming out of the Father.

00:20:37.600 --> 00:20:46.959
One individual said, "Is a blue flame hotter than any other flame?"I thought it would be red because things get red hot.

00:20:46.960 --> 00:20:59.377
I said that's what happens to metal after its acceleration of heat, but a torch flame is blue. The hotter the flame, the bluer it is.

00:20:59.378 --> 00:21:09.759
And I saw the blue coming out, looking like sapphires coming out of the Lord, feeding the individual with the Holy Ghost and fire.

00:21:09.760 --> 00:21:13.599
And the Lord said, "It's time for the Body of Christ to get hot.

00:21:13.600 --> 00:21:20.832
It's time for the remnant, for His eyes are running to and fro throughout the whole earth.

00:21:20.833 --> 00:21:35.519
And He's choosing right now. His gaze is upon His generals. His gaze is upon the remnant.

00:21:35.520 --> 00:21:43.718
And this is the final selection time, like it was with Gideon's army."Joshua's army?

00:21:43.719 --> 00:21:50.879
No. When they were drinking down the water, He said they lap it up; they're 300 strong.

00:21:50.880 --> 00:21:55.519
It doesn't take a lot to take a nation; it just needs obedience.

00:21:55.520 --> 00:22:04.158
It just needs somebody to say, "Hey, I'm yielded."So what I'm trying to tell you is right now God is making His final cuts.

00:22:04.159 --> 00:22:13.918
He's making His final selections. Will you make the cut? For many are called, but few are chosen.

00:22:13.919 --> 00:22:18.649
That's what He said. "Many are called, Brandon, but few are chosen.

00:22:18.650 --> 00:22:23.519
I have called a vast number of you, but will you make the final cut?

00:22:23.520 --> 00:22:49.279
Will you make the final cut for what God is going to do in being a leader for Him in this end-time move?"And He said that to me: "As many are called, but few have been chosen to lead this last push."I am selecting this new dream team, what I call the basketball like it was in the Olympics.

00:22:49.280 --> 00:23:02.339
He said, "I'm selecting my dream team. I'm bringing forth the end-time voices that are dead to self, that are alive unto me, and that are attached to me.

00:23:02.340 --> 00:23:14.719
For those that have been cut off, I saw an umbilical cord wrapped around their feet and they were dead."And there was an Ichabod upon them. I saw an Ichabod. And the Lord said, "Don't be one of these.

00:23:14.720 --> 00:23:27.999
Don't be like other men."When Oral Roberts went to school and he was up in Enid, Oklahoma, going to Bible school, he walked out and the Lord said, "Oral, don't be like these other men.

00:23:28.000 --> 00:23:33.459
Separate yourself unto me."He talks about it all the time: "Who are you attached to?

00:23:33.460 --> 00:23:42.239
Are you attached to me?"Don't worry about all these other people. You do what I tell you to do and you say what I tell you to say.

00:23:42.240 --> 00:23:49.199
So right now He's making His final selections of His remnant, His warriors.

00:23:49.200 --> 00:23:56.936
Right now the eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth looking for a heart that is perfect toward Him.

00:23:56.937 --> 00:24:08.586
Who are the end-time generals? Who are the end-time faces? The new Davids, the new Hannahs, the new Esthers, whoever will be the ones that say, "Here am I, Lord.

00:24:08.587 --> 00:24:20.178
Use me."As the angel takes the coal out of the fire and places it upon the lips, will you be one of the ones that God can use because you have a clean heart?

00:24:20.179 --> 00:24:25.119
"Create in me a clean heart, Lord. I want to be the apple of your eye.

00:24:25.120 --> 00:24:31.998
Hide me under the shadow of thy wings."And that's what the Lord has been talking to me about for the last 24 hours.

00:24:31.999 --> 00:24:35.599
He said, "I'm making my selections. I'm looking upon my troops.

00:24:35.600 --> 00:24:44.478
I'm looking upon my bride right now."And He goes, "Many are called, but few are chosen."Many are called, Brandon, but few are chosen.

00:24:44.479 --> 00:25:02.079
I'm looking to see: do you make the cut? I'm never going to be arrogant enough to say, "Well, of course I qualify."He's examining the people right now.

00:25:02.080 --> 00:25:08.052
That's what He said to me. And you're about to see nobodies get a huge platform and become somebodies overnight.

00:25:08.053 --> 00:25:11.187
And the people who thought they were something, they're going to be humbled.

00:25:11.188 --> 00:25:17.096
There's a humbling coming to so much arrogance in the Body of Christ.

00:25:17.097 --> 00:25:24.178
You think you're greater than others and you don't deflect; you have a big head, but it's not about you.

00:25:24.179 --> 00:25:28.959
It's about Him. And the Lord said they've not deflected. They've not been obedient.

00:25:28.960 --> 00:25:33.644
They whine. They complain. It's not about having a cushion in the bank.

00:25:33.645 --> 00:25:40.479
It's about doing the Great Commission and bringing in the souls because Jesus Christ is coming.

00:25:40.480 --> 00:25:53.359
He said, "I'm leaving the ninety-nine and I'm going after the one."And there's so much lukewarm and there's so much stagnant in the Body of Christ, and it is a stench to our Father.

00:25:53.360 --> 00:26:10.319
It's time to arise and shine for the light has come and the glory of the Lord is risen on us to take this gospel into all the highways and the byways and telling people that Jesus Christ is coming and He's coming sooner than you think.

00:26:10.320 --> 00:26:21.999
Diana had a prophetic dream and the rain was coming. People weren't paying attention. As there was rain rising as in the days of Noah, so will it be.

00:26:22.000 --> 00:26:27.438
The rain was coming and people didn't see that the signs of the times were happening all around.

00:26:27.439 --> 00:26:32.798
The water level was rising, and she said, "It's time to get in the plane. Jesus is coming.

00:26:32.799 --> 00:26:38.283
We've got to get in the plane."And the dream was so detailed about where we are right now.

00:26:38.284 --> 00:26:44.319
She said there were so many people that were not prepared for what was happening on the earth.

00:26:44.320 --> 00:26:55.199
The rain came and they drowned. It was symbolic. Are you ready for the soon return of the Lord? Are you lukewarm?

00:26:55.200 --> 00:27:01.074
He'd rather you be hot or cold, but I'm telling you, He's looking for a people who are hot for Him.

